title: 911 Media Footage Pack 9/11
description:
This a collection of the 911 media footage that I converted from the originalmpg files a few years ago. These files were converted and combined using virtualdubmod and nandub and sony soundforge. They are best viewed in the original window size of 640x480. If you try and make them fullscreen, especially on modern day 1920x1200 monitors, they will appear very poor quality. But this is the highest quality 911 media footage that has ever been made available online in such a small size.

 This is to acknowledge 12 years since the world was duped by media fakery and global psychological manipulation.
